Entry.JapaneseText: 特に、大きな争いがあるようには 見えないわね……
Entry.EnglishText: It doesn't seem like there are any huge fights breaking out here...

Entry.JapaneseText: でもなんかイヤーな雰囲気だぜ。 話を聞いてみたほうがいいんじゃないか？
Entry.EnglishText: It still feels like something's wrong, though. Shouldn't we go ask everyone what's going on?
